                <note rend="inline" type="source">837.51/876: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Representative on Special Mission in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Crowder</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-10-28T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 28, 1922—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>73. Your telegram No. 72, October 24, 6 p.m.</p>
                <p>Governor Harding has arranged to leave Washington November 1, arriving Habana
                    November 3, 5 p.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
